{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"c8f43c62-abd3-5cd4-b247-c270f9204cfd","html":"<p><strong>作为一个商城的项目主要的功能有：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>登录、登出</li>\n<li>查看商品列表，看看单个商品详情。</li>\n<li>添加商品到购物车，修改购物车信息。</li>\n<li>下订单、结算。</li>\n<li>查看订单信息。</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>根据功能，可能需要这些页面：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>登录页</li>\n<li>注册页</li>\n<li>商品列表页</li>\n<li>商品详情页</li>\n<li>购物车页</li>\n<li>订单信息页</li>\n<li>其他页面</li>\n</ul>\n<p>确定这些信息后，可以尝试设计一下这些页面之间是如何进行交互及跳转的了。\n大致的交互如下图：\n<img src=\"https://github.com/GoWantong/GoWantong.github.io/raw/master/assets/img/prototype.png\" alt=\"prototype\"></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"用React构建一个小商城（一）","date":"08月 10日, 2017年"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/blog/2017-08-10-react-shop-summary-start/","previous":{"id":"f6f60204-6996-5f5a-8d5e-33d3186b054f","fields":{"slug":"/blog/2017-06-10-brain-and-knowledge/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"猜想，大脑和知识的关系","tags":["学习","头脑风暴","猜想"],"date":"2017-06-10T00:00:00.000Z","cover":null}},"next":{"id":"c49b5fd3-de90-509c-82ec-37f4763eb90d","fields":{"slug":"/blog/2017-08-11-react-shop-summary-ui/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"用React构建一个小商城（二）","tags":["web","学习","前端","React"],"date":"2017-08-11T00:00:00.000Z","cover":"https://github.com/GoWantong/GoWantong.github.io/raw/master/assets/img/google-play-carousel.png"}}}}